# Getting Started
 1-To get started, fork this repository to your GitHub account.
 2-Clone the repo.
 3-Install packages.
 4-Add OpenWeatherMap API KEY on lib/src/core/utils/secrets.dart

A new Flutter project.
- Flutter
- openweathermap API
- Bloc State management
- Local Database

## Features

- get Weather of Current Location
- get hourly weather details
- get weather forecast of next 7 days
- search weather of city
- get weather history of 5 previous days

Note : Change Api Key from

